      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TULHURST PEBBLES (2) has been competitive of late and kept the ball rolling last time when 3.5 metres from the winner in fourth over 1660m at Albion Park. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Meets a similar line up and she can figure in the finish. FAVREAU (3) is in good form at present. Finished third at his latest appearance over 2040m at this track, beaten 5 metres. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. It doesn't get any easier but on his best form he is good enough to take this out. DIEGO DELGADO (1) is better than his last-start seventh over 2040m here. Can bounce back from the favourable draw. MISTER DELWIN (7) must be considered after he finished runner-up over 2040m at this course a week ago. Top-three candidate.",
